text: Ong Sai Hung (born 21 February 1999 in Perlis) is a Malaysian professional squash player. He attended SJKC Chung Hwa Jitra. As of October 2019, he was ranked number 174 in the world. He has competed in the main draw of multiple professional PSA tournaments.
